❌ **Custom Authorization Mechanisms**: Must use standard patterns

## Emergency Procedures

### System Shutdown
```python
# Graceful shutdown
await orchestrator.stop_all_components()

# Emergency shutdown
await risk_manager.emergency_shutdown()
await execution_engine.cancel_all_executions()
```

### Risk Limit Breaches
```python
# Automatic risk controls
if portfolio_risk > risk_limits['max_var']:
    await risk_manager.reduce_positions()
    
if position_concentration > limits['max_concentration']:
    await risk_manager.rebalance_portfolio()
```

